@startuml
title Use Case: Report Incident

usecase "Report Incident" as UC
actor "Civilian" as C
actor "Dispatcher" as D

C --> UC : Initiates report
D --> UC : Receives & logs
note right of UC
  ID: UC-001
  Priority: High
  Description: Citizen reports
  a crime or incident
  Precondition: System active
  Postcondition: Incident logged
end note

UC .> (Enter Details) : include
UC .> (Verify Location) : include
UC .> (Assign Priority) : extend
@enduml
